Dialogue: 0,00:00:26.40,00:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:28.90,00:00:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:30.86,00:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God. \NChristopher, can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:35.12,00:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:36.66,00:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sharon! \N- She's there.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:42.04,00:00:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:45.54,00:00:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:50.47,00:00:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:53.47,00:00:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:15.32,00:01:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:22.92,00:01:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:35.76,00:01:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon! Honey!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.78,00:01:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God. Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:53.99,00:01:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:56.11,00:01:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.53,00:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.67,00:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Home! Home! \N- We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.04,00:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Silent Hill!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:11.09,00:02:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Silent Hill! \N- Rose!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:13.97,00:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wake up. \N- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:16.09,00:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's okay, sweetie. We're here now. \N- It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:18.97,00:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:21.89,00:02:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, baby. \NWe're going right home.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:24.60,00:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are we gonna do? \N- We'll get there.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:27.44,00:02:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find a way through this. \NWe'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:30.52,00:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:32.69,00:02:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- She said it again. \N- I know.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:37.57,00:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on, baby. It's okay. \N- Calm down, baby. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:41.91,00:02:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's okay, baby. \N- We're right here.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:47.62,00:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:50.42,00:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:54.38,00:02:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, baby.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:59.22,00:03:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,SILENT HILL
Dialogue: 0,00:03:23.37,00:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wanna see? \N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:26.58,00:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there, pumpkin?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:32.59,00:03:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an amazing lion. \NDid you do that all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:36.84,00:03:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so impressed with you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:46.06,00:03:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know we're going \Non a special trip, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:51.44,00:03:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:55.11,00:03:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.78,00:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, sometimes when you go \Nto sleep, you go on a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:00.53,00:04:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes \Nyou talk about a place...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:04.62,00:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...called Silent Hill.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:08.46,00:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:11.29,00:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:13.29,00:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're gonna go there, \Nso you can remember.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:26.10,00:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:30.31,00:04:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sweetie. \NIt's gonna be just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:17.02,00:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Break's over, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:19.90,00:05:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You awake?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:22.70,00:05:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:31.37,00:05:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not know that we will judge angels? \NDo you not know that the saints will judge the world?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:36.38,00:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Corinthians 6:2-3
Dialogue: 0,00:05:43.05,00:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, Rose. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:49.06,00:05:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Hi, this is Rose Da Silva.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:05:51.39,00:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Please leave a message, \Nand I'll call you back.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:06:05.57,00:06:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,GHOST TOWN OF AMERICA
Dialogue: 0,00:06:12.50,00:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,SILENT HILL \NWEST VIRGINIA
Dialogue: 0,00:06:13.62,00:06:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.42,00:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Silent Hill: The Tainted Town
Dialogue: 0,00:07:36.58,00:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:38.83,00:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Long drive.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:40.25,00:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:45.01,00:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you change your pictures?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:50.01,00:07:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:51.85,00:07:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mommy? \N- You can't remember?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:54.06,00:07:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't like that, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:57.48,00:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Baby, you can't remember doing this? \N- Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:01.23,00:08:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, hey, baby, it's okay. \N- Mommy, who did that?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:04.48,00:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, honey. Mommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:08.15,00:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you wait in the car for me?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:10.49,00:08:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I sit in front?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:13.53,00:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course you can sit in the front. \N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:29.38,00:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy, we need \Na ham and cheese on white.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:31.89,00:08:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:34.39,00:08:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanna pay for the gas.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:37.27,00:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And can you tell me the best way \Nto get to Silent Hill?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:40.56,00:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to find it on the map.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:43.73,00:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why do you wanna go there? \N- I...I read about it.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:47.82,00:08:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Road don't go through no more.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:50.86,00:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your card was declined.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:56.41,00:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:58.25,00:09:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is everything all right? \N- Don't talk to strangers.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:04.42,00:09:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:06.04,00:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Well, thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:13.76,00:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you cut off the cards?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:15.64,00:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>That's not gonna stop me \Nfrom taking her there.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:17.89,00:09:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, honey, \Nwe gotta put Sharon in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:21.14,00:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>She needs constant care, \Nand she needs medication.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:23.81,00:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The medication doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:26.44,00:09:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's getting worse every day.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:29.78,00:09:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, the adoption people said \NSharon came from West Virginia...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:33.70,00:09:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>...and Silent Hill is in West Virginia.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:35.82,00:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I'm not giving up on her, Chris. \NI'm not.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:37.87,00:09:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you actually read \Nthe websites, Rose?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:39.12,00:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Yes, Chris, I read them.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:42.96,00:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trust me on this, please? \NJust trust me on this.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:47.34,00:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Listen, honey...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:48.50,00:09:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- I love Sharon every bit as much as I... \N- Chris, I gotta go.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:54.18,00:09:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...I love you.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:56.09,00:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Need any help, ma'am? \N- No, we're...We're fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:02.85,00:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:19.89,00:11:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we there?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:22.39,00:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet, honey.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:36.32,00:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your seatbelt fastened.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:39.99,00:11:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:01.34,00:12:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:34.46,00:12:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's just the radio.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:37.17,00:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm turning it off. \N- Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:30.89,00:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:38.82,00:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:41.90,00:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Help!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:44.61,00:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:49.12,00:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had an accident!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:56.13,00:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:06.30,00:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon. Honey.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:21.73,00:14:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashes.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:35.71,00:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,WELCOME TO SILENT HILL
Dialogue: 0,00:15:36.93,00:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:44.19,00:15:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:45.99,00:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:48.15,00:15:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:49.74,00:15:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:14.76,00:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:20.27,00:16:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:29.07,00:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:18.41,00:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:26.67,00:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Mommy.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:17:29.88,00:17:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:06.50,00:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:21.22,00:18:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:50.46,00:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:13.82,00:19:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:17.99,00:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:19.53,00:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:22.95,00:19:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:46.02,00:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:51.44,00:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:53.32,00:19:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me. Help.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:55.99,00:19:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:01.87,00:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:35.98,00:20:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:37.57,00:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:39.07,00:20:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:43.53,00:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Get off me! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:59.51,00:21:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off...!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:52.12,00:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the dark one opens \Nand closes the door to Silent Hill.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:56.08,00:22:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:59.04,00:23:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's happening. \NDo you know what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,00:23:04.55,00:23:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:06.72,00:23:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for my daughter. \NI'm afraid that she's been hurt.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:09.60,00:23:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all lost our children.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:12.22,00:23:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Our light.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:15.06,00:23:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They deceived me.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:17.23,00:23:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Their evil.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:19.15,00:23:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Their hate.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:23.73,00:23:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They hurt my child.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:26.07,00:23:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They did terrible things to her.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:29.37,00:23:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alessa.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:33.08,00:23:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my daughter, Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:35.45,00:23:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She sleepwalks, \Nso you have to be careful...
Dialogue: 0,00:23:37.58,00:23:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...but if you see her, \Nplease, tell her to wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:43.13,00:23:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's mine.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:46.05,00:23:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was mine. \N- It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:47.43,00:23:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's mine. \N- It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,00:23:49.43,00:23:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's mine! \N- Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,00:23:58.98,00:24:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,lnto the fire \Nshe swallowed their hate.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:30.80,00:24:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hi there. \N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:35.18,00:24:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, my wife, \Nshe came through here last night.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:38.93,00:24:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe you saw her? \N- Daughter worked night shift.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:43.81,00:24:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, she was heading \Nfor this place, Silent Hill.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:49.11,00:24:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- How do I get there? \N- You don't.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:51.49,00:24:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Town's closed down \Nbecause of the coal fire...
Dialogue: 0,00:24:53.66,00:24:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...still burning underground, \Nyou know?
Dialogue: 0,00:24:56.33,00:24:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe enough of them fumes, \Noh, bound to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,00:25:01.92,00:25:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,00:25:04.96,00:25:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...where's the turnoff?
Dialogue: 0,00:25:20.02,00:25:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,00:25:53.76,00:25:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:02.39,00:26:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Hi, this is Chris. \NPlease leave a message.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:26:06.19,00:26:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Christopher, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:08.82,00:26:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in Silent Hill. \NI'm sorry, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:12.53,00:26:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon's lost, \Nbut I think I know where she is...
Dialogue: 0,00:26:14.99,00:26:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I'm going to the school \Nto look for her.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:19.29,00:26:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not okay, all right? \NI need your help.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:22.16,00:26:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:28.67,00:26:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,00:26:29.92,00:26:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, I want you to put \Nboth hands on the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:35.09,00:26:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Put both hands on the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:39.72,00:26:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the little girl, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,00:26:42.10,00:26:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, my daughter, she's gone. \NI need your help.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:45.52,00:26:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get out of the car. \N- What?
Dialogue: 0,00:26:47.69,00:26:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:50.44,00:26:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,00:26:52.28,00:26:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're under arrest. \N- What?
Dialogue: 0,00:26:54.61,00:26:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you say can and will be \Nused against you in a court of law.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:57.78,00:27:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you understand. \NThere's something weird going on.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:00.78,00:27:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter, she's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:02.49,00:27:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really cared, \Nyou wouldn't have sped off.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:04.79,00:27:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, she 's ill. \NShe sleepwalks.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:07.25,00:27:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calm right down. \NI'm gonna find the little girl.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:11.96,00:27:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer Bennett to base, over.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:16.30,00:27:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Base, do you copy, over?
Dialogue: 0,00:27:18.97,00:27:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shit. \N- You're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:26.31,00:27:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cracked my head on the road \Npretty good...
Dialogue: 0,00:27:28.31,00:27:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...when my bike went down. \NI must have been out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:32.19,00:27:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- You all right to walk? \N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:35.69,00:27:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it looks like we'll be \Nhiking back to Brahams.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:38.49,00:27:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,00:27:41.08,00:27:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going back to the station.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:42.99,00:27:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you kidding? \N- Nope.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:45.08,00:27:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard \Na single word I've said?
Dialogue: 0,00:27:47.87,00:27:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I hear you. \N- Have you heard...
Dialogue: 0,00:27:49.67,00:27:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...a single word I've said?
Dialogue: 0,00:27:52.09,00:27:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's at the school, \Nwe just need to turn around...
Dialogue: 0,00:27:54.96,00:27:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>...Silent Hill... \N...sorry...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:27:57.97,00:27:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>...Sharon... \N...lost...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:27:59.72,00:28:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>...think I know where... \N...going to the school to look for her...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:28:05.52,00:28:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I'm not okay...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:28:07.18,00:28:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I need your...Your help. \NPlease, hurry!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:28:29.16,00:28:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir, this road is closed. \NYou'll have to turn around.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:32.13,00:28:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for my wife. \NShe may have come through here.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:35.84,00:28:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She drives a Jeep Liberty. \NSilver, Ohio plates.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:41.09,00:28:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, this man's wife \Nwas driving the Jeep.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:45.72,00:28:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Bring him down.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:28:46.89,00:28:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on. \N- You've seen her?
Dialogue: 0,00:28:55.07,00:28:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,00:28:56.82,00:28:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,lnspector Thomas Gucci. \NEnjoying the weather, are you?
Dialogue: 0,00:28:59.40,00:29:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For God's sake, \NI'm trying to find my wife.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:01.86,00:29:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:03.28,00:29:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that vehicle you were \Ntalking about, we found it.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:05.87,00:29:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at the end of the bridge here, \Nbut it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:08.29,00:29:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no indication \Nanyone's come under any harm.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:10.08,00:29:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good Christ. \N- Now, you mind telling me...
Dialogue: 0,00:29:13.00,00:29:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...what your wife's doing \Nup here, Mr...?
Dialogue: 0,00:29:15.17,00:29:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Da Silva, Chris Da Silva. \N- My pleasure, Chris...
Dialogue: 0,00:29:17.46,00:29:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The faster we start looking, \Nthe faster we're gonna find her.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:20.34,00:29:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, hold your horses, \Nhold your horses, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:23.01,00:29:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also got a missing deputy.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:25.26,00:29:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And knowing Officer Cybil Bennett \Nthe way I do...
Dialogue: 0,00:29:27.60,00:29:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...she's probably out there looking \Nfor your wife and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:30.56,00:29:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bobby, make sure no one \Ncomes through that barricade.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:33.06,00:29:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get our asses up \Nto Silent Hill.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:35.15,00:29:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's take a look around. \N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:36.94,00:29:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,While Chris here tells me \Nwhat's going on.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:40.86,00:29:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She disappeared yesterday. \NI spoke to her...
Dialogue: 0,00:29:43.70,00:29:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...when she stopped for gas \Nin Brahams.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:46.07,00:29:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you coming up here \Nin the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,00:29:48.66,00:29:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- I thought it would help her. \N- You people. You get off the highway...
Dialogue: 0,00:29:52.29,00:29:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...from whatever big city, bringing \Nall your sick problems with you.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:57.79,00:30:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,00:30:00.34,00:30:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a guy come up here \Ntwo years ago...
Dialogue: 0,00:30:02.84,00:30:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...snatched a little boy from a rest stop, \Ndropped him into a mine vent.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:06.30,00:30:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanna see \Nanything like that again.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:08.35,00:30:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I don't know what \Nyou're thinking, but you're not helping.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:11.35,00:30:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way I would ever \Nharm my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:13.73,00:30:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I even know \Nshe is your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,00:30:16.27,00:30:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:22.65,00:30:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,00:31:00.44,00:31:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:02.36,00:31:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you see \Nwhat I'm talking about?
Dialogue: 0,00:31:04.78,00:31:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take these handcuffs \Noff me?
Dialogue: 0,00:31:06.57,00:31:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Get walking.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:09.20,00:31:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a fire-Iookout tower \Non the far side of Toluca Lake.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:12.04,00:31:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- It should have a radio. \N- Fuck you, you stupid cop.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:15.37,00:31:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is completely cut off.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:19.04,00:31:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- You have no idea what's going on. \N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,00:31:22.71,00:31:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you up there!
Dialogue: 0,00:31:26.05,00:31:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a police officer!
Dialogue: 0,00:31:32.22,00:31:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,00:31:41.57,00:31:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,00:31:47.91,00:31:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:52.74,00:31:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, shoot it.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:08.22,00:32:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,00:32:11.43,00:32:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,00:33:51.07,00:33:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,MIDWICH ELEMENTARY SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,00:34:05.83,00:34:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:18.60,00:34:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The foes of the righteous will be condemned
Dialogue: 0,00:34:45.17,00:34:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,MAIN OFFICE
Dialogue: 0,00:35:36.30,00:35:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Rose.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:49.10,00:35:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,COUNTRY
Dialogue: 0,00:35:51.11,00:35:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,HOME
Dialogue: 0,00:35:53.07,00:35:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,LOYALTY
Dialogue: 0,00:35:54.90,00:35:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD
Dialogue: 0,00:35:57.65,00:35:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Mrs. Da Silva, \NI am an officer of the law...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:36:00.12,00:36:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>...and I will take you to safety.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:36:02.20,00:36:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Mrs. Da Silva, \NI am an officer of the law...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:36:05.29,00:36:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>...and I will take you to safety.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:36:07.46,00:36:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why don't you let me do that? \N- Ninety percent of the time...
Dialogue: 0,00:36:10.33,00:36:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...when a wife takes a run...
Dialogue: 0,00:36:11.88,00:36:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...she takes the daughter \Nto a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,00:36:14.34,00:36:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd say she's damn mad \Nat her husband.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:18.01,00:36:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You like hauling skeletons \Nout of your family closet?
Dialogue: 0,00:36:20.51,00:36:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not all the time, but we're \Ndriving on top of them right now.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:24.18,00:36:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Coal fire's still burning \Nunderneath.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:26.81,00:36:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the barbershop over there?
Dialogue: 0,00:36:29.19,00:36:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Used to be my father's. \N- Your father?
Dialogue: 0,00:36:33.19,00:36:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:35.36,00:36:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,November '74, \Nwhen the fire caught.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:37.94,00:36:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They tried to evacuate this place \Nas quick as they could...
Dialogue: 0,00:36:41.49,00:36:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it was hellish, people were \Ndying and disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:44.66,00:36:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell, they couldn't even find \Nhalf the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:47.54,00:36:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the end of Silent Hill.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:49.33,00:36:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,These were good people, \Nmost of them.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:52.79,00:36:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Some, you might say deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:55.30,00:36:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:12.73,00:37:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:46.28,00:38:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:47.87,00:38:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,WITCH
Dialogue: 0,00:38:51.91,00:38:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,00:39:11.39,00:39:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,00:39:40.17,00:39:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:42.17,00:39:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:44.38,00:39:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:51.30,00:39:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me. Oh, God. \NPlease, please, help me. Help...
Dialogue: 0,00:39:59.06,00:40:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me. Please, help me. \NHelp me. Help me, please.
Dialogue: 0,00:40:58.37,00:41:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening again.
Dialogue: 0,00:42:07.69,00:42:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,00:42:24.37,00:42:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose!
Dialogue: 0,00:42:27.71,00:42:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,00:42:33.22,00:42:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose!
Dialogue: 0,00:43:38.99,00:43:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose!
Dialogue: 0,00:43:51.50,00:43:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:08.64,00:44:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rose! \N- Put your mask on.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:11.06,00:44:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,00:44:19.95,00:44:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- I felt her. \N- You what?
Dialogue: 0,00:44:22.70,00:44:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Her perfume.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:25.41,00:44:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- She was here. \N- Who was?
Dialogue: 0,00:44:26.08,00:44:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- My wife. \N- She wasn't here. Put this mask on.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:29.25,00:44:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Perfume. \N- Breathe. Through that mask.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:33.50,00:44:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go. \NWe're gonna go this way.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:36.30,00:44:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chris, come on.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:40.09,00:44:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- She was here. \N- No, no, she wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:42.18,00:44:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:58.95,00:44:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:00.41,00:45:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:28.68,00:45:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off! Get off! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,00:45:34.69,00:45:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me that pipe.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:37.48,00:45:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose, the pipe!
Dialogue: 0,00:45:40.74,00:45:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:44.49,00:45:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- I got it. I got it. \N- Quick, come on!
Dialogue: 0,00:46:02.63,00:46:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,00:46:04.97,00:46:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:07.18,00:46:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Last mag.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:08.85,00:46:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's all the bullets you got? \N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:14.23,00:46:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:27.95,00:46:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,00:46:37.21,00:46:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:44.38,00:46:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay down! Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,00:46:46.59,00:46:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:50.31,00:46:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,00:46:59.27,00:47:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:47:53.49,00:47:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,00:48:34.16,00:48:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,00:48:37.25,00:48:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,00:48:40.54,00:48:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw that, right? \NThat was real?
Dialogue: 0,00:48:45.71,00:48:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,00:48:47.34,00:48:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I know this is crazy. I know.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:50.26,00:48:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta calm right down, \Nbecause my kid is not here...
Dialogue: 0,00:48:52.85,00:48:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I've gotta find her \Nbefore this happens again.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:56.56,00:48:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:59.06,00:49:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:00.94,00:49:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:03.11,00:49:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where it is, \Nbut she is in this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:06.78,00:49:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:15.24,00:49:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:19.04,00:49:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:34.01,00:49:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, don't be trying \Nanything, all right?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:36.10,00:49:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We got men up here \Nall night long.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:38.31,00:49:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna find your wife, \Nwe're gonna find your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:41.23,00:49:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't have civilians \Nwandering around on their own.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:44.81,00:49:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not telling me everything.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:48.23,00:49:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What really happened up here?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:49.74,00:49:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:55.28,00:49:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Directory assistance. \N- Toluca County Archives, please.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:49:57.87,00:49:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>One moment.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:49:59.70,00:50:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Archives? \N- Yeah, listen.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:02.25,00:50:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the records there \Nfrom Silent Hill?
Dialogue: 0,00:50:05.04,00:50:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Which records, sir? \N- The police records.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:08.38,00:50:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Sorry, sir, \Nthose records are confidential.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:11.01,00:50:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I can't... \NNo, listen, I...
Dialogue: 0,00:50:13.38,00:50:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Sorry, sir, \NI can't access that information.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:15.80,00:50:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Listen, goddamn it. \N- Sir.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:17.47,00:50:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- This is an emergency. \N- I can't...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:19.06,00:50:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I can't help you.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:37.32,00:50:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They used to say \Nthis place was haunted.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:40.66,00:50:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they were right.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:43.29,00:50:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,GRAND HOTEL
Dialogue: 0,00:50:52.21,00:50:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Help! No!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:55.01,00:50:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Stay away. \N- Come on.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:57.05,00:50:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away, sinner.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:00.14,00:51:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,00:51:03.68,00:51:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:07.23,00:51:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith is our destroyer. \NFaith has brought us doom.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:10.27,00:51:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get back! \N- Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,00:51:11.69,00:51:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get back! \N- Hey, stop.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:14.82,00:51:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you of thee \Nwho cast the first stone.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:17.41,00:51:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lambs without a shepherd, \Nshepherd without a flock.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:20.41,00:51:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your sins which hold you here.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:22.70,00:51:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop your lies! \N- Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:24.46,00:51:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:25.62,00:51:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're not gonna hurt you. \N- She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:28.75,00:51:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:30.67,00:51:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna. My name is Anna.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:34.42,00:51:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here, Anna? \NWho was that?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:36.68,00:51:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've seen her before. \N- Dahlia was cast out.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:39.93,00:51:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the darkness wants her.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:42.22,00:51:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's lost her daughter too. \N- What?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:45.02,00:51:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sinners deserve to lose their spawn. \N- What are you doing here, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:52.15,00:51:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother needs more food.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:55.32,00:51:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean there are \Nother people here?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:00.03,00:52:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Christabella keeps us safe.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:02.20,00:52:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Anna. \N- We take refuge in the church.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:05.16,00:52:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:08.62,00:52:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost my daughter. \NShe's all alone.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:11.34,00:52:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine how frightened \Nshe must feel?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:14.21,00:52:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, have you seen her?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:16.38,00:52:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:21.55,00:52:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If she has faith, she might survive.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:24.68,00:52:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If not...
Dialogue: 0,00:52:28.64,00:52:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:32.06,00:52:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:34.36,00:52:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it at the school.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:37.19,00:52:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on all the buildings \Nthe elders of my elders built.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:41.16,00:52:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a symbol of our unity, \Na symbol of our faith.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:57.09,00:52:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:00.84,00:53:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it? \N- Just like yours.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:05.43,00:53:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where did you find it? \N- They're all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:23.16,00:53:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:25.12,00:53:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:28.54,00:53:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- What number did you take this from? \N- 111.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:34.67,00:53:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta go to room 111.
Dialogue: 0,00:54:42.99,00:54:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,SILENT HILL POLICE RECORDS
Dialogue: 0,00:55:10.51,00:55:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gucci.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:42.67,00:55:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Directory assistance. \N- Yeah.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:55:45.34,00:55:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Toluca County Orphanage, please.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:48.09,00:55:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>One moment, please.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:55:52.01,00:55:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Yes, I have that information for you. \N- Yeah.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:55:55.31,00:55:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me that address?
Dialogue: 0,00:56:06.32,00:56:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We are wandering far \Nfrom refuge here.
Dialogue: 0,00:56:12.08,00:56:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep her with us. \NShe's all we got.
Dialogue: 0,00:56:42.23,00:56:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no room 111.
Dialogue: 0,00:56:44.07,00:56:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The first burning.
Dialogue: 0,00:56:47.36,00:56:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it, Anna? \N- The first burning.
Dialogue: 0,00:56:51.07,00:56:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the town had a name.
Dialogue: 0,00:56:53.20,00:56:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The elders of my elders \Nkept us pure.
Dialogue: 0,00:56:57.25,00:56:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The founders of this town \Nwere witch- hunters.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:00.08,00:57:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Burning the witch \Nheld back the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:02.75,00:57:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped the apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:10.30,00:57:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:28.28,00:57:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a room in here.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:41.92,00:57:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:51.51,00:57:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:53.76,00:57:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:10.57,00:58:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,00:58:12.99,00:58:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. \NWe're in the next building.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:15.37,00:58:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Some factory, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,00:58:19.16,00:58:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there was a fire.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:50.40,00:58:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose!
Dialogue: 0,00:59:22.89,00:59:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,00:59:37.16,00:59:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:40.16,00:59:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared. \NI promise I'm not gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,01:00:01.76,01:00:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose?
Dialogue: 0,01:00:25.29,01:00:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,01:00:27.79,01:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,01:00:33.80,01:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,01:00:41.60,01:00:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,01:00:50.40,01:00:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,01:00:51.90,01:00:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:04.37,01:01:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:06.24,01:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be her twin.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:12.50,01:01:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Alessa?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:16.25,01:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:19.05,01:01:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:22.34,01:01:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm burning.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:27.14,01:01:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:31.52,01:01:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose? My God.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:33.56,01:01:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- How did you get over there? \N- Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:40.45,01:01:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab onto it.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:43.24,01:01:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now swing back around. \N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:51.62,01:01:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you all right? \N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:53.38,01:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell \Nwere you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:55.29,01:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:57.55,01:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just saw Dahlia's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:01.38,01:02:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the one \Nthat brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:03.26,01:02:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,01:02:04.72,01:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the one \Nthat made me crash my car.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:07.85,01:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alessa.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:09.22,01:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't say her name.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:15.23,01:02:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the seal, isn't it, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,01:02:18.73,01:02:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The symbol of your faith?
Dialogue: 0,01:02:23.86,01:02:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Something terrible happened here.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:30.29,01:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to leave. \NWe have to leave!
Dialogue: 0,01:02:34.75,01:02:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- The darkness is coming! \N- Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:37.42,01:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,01:02:50.81,01:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The church isn't far.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:53.27,01:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Run. Run! \N- Rose, come on!
Dialogue: 0,01:02:55.35,01:02:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose!
Dialogue: 0,01:03:06.95,01:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,01:03:15.79,01:03:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:17.17,01:03:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come! \N- We gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:37.31,01:03:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rose, come on. \N- I've seen this.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:50.91,01:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,01:03:54.70,01:03:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cybil! \N- Rose, come on.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:05.30,01:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cybil!
Dialogue: 0,01:04:06.47,01:04:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You run not towards sanctuary \Nbut from your fears.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:09.51,01:04:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not join the others. \NThey are deceivers. They are damned.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:12.47,01:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- We gotta get inside. \N- No!
Dialogue: 0,01:04:14.22,01:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They are wolves \Nin the skin of sheep.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:16.02,01:04:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They brought about their own hell. \NThey'll take you with them.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:19.02,01:04:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Filth and lies! \N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,01:04:21.48,01:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,01:04:24.19,01:04:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. I've seen your daughter. \NI've seen Alessa.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:30.37,01:04:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's coming! \N- She's dead, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,01:04:33.16,01:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire doesn't cleanse, it blackens.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:35.33,01:04:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Listen to me. \N- Rose, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,01:04:37.71,01:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks exactly like Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:39.96,01:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She brought us here, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,01:04:46.13,01:04:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,01:04:48.55,01:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil wakes in vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:50.39,01:04:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful what you choose.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:12.99,01:05:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:03.75,01:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- No. \N- Send them back!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:06.34,01:06:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:08.30,01:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lost.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:20.06,01:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:31.57,01:06:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Christabella, \Nthey lured my Anna.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:35.24,01:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave her to the fiend.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:38.03,01:06:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleanor, you must remember \Nthat Anna went against our laws.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:41.83,01:06:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She went alone outside \Ninto the devil's playground.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:46.75,01:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She was not the responsibility \Nof these two strangers.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:52.01,01:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll deal with them later.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:00.10,01:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we must pray.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:17.03,01:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,REVELATION 20:11-15
Dialogue: 0,01:07:23.04,01:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I saw them...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:24.46,01:07:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...from whose presence \Nearth and heaven fled away.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:28.29,01:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And no home was left to them.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:31.09,01:07:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I saw them...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:33.38,01:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...from whose presence \Nearth and heaven fled away.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:36.84,01:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And no home was left to them.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:40.01,01:07:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw the dead, \Nthe great and the small...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:42.97,01:07:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they were judged \Naccording to their deeds.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:46.31,01:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw the dead, \Nthe great and the small...
Dialogue: 0,01:07:51.57,01:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they were judged \Naccording to their deeds.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:57.32,01:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyone's name not found \Nwritten in the book of life...
Dialogue: 0,01:08:01.87,01:08:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...they will be thrown \Ninto the lake of fire.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:13.88,01:08:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Toluca County Orphanage
Dialogue: 0,01:08:15.51,01:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I lay me down to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,01:08:18.59,01:08:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...I pray the Lord my soul to keep.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:21.68,01:08:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I should die before I wake...
Dialogue: 0,01:08:24.68,01:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...I pray the Lord my soul to take.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:28.14,01:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:30.36,01:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, girls, into bed. \NQuickly, now.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:33.32,01:08:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No better place to be \Non a rainy night.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:36.11,01:08:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In you go, Lindsey, thattagirl. \NYou've got your bear, that's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:39.70,01:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No talking \Nafter lights are out.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:45.87,01:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, children.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:47.08,01:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And God bless.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:54.00,01:08:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sister Margaret, \Nthis really can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:57.38,01:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine why.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:01.14,01:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years ago...
Dialogue: 0,01:09:03.14,01:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...a baby was left \Noutside this orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:05.35,01:09:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife and I were the ones \Nwho adopted her.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:07.64,01:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy for you, \NMr. Da Silva...
Dialogue: 0,01:09:10.65,01:09:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I can't give out \Ninformation on our children.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:16.07,01:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:18.74,01:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl, she looks \Nexactly like my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:20.99,01:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help you, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:24.12,01:09:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's late. \N- She must be 40 now.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:26.95,01:09:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I find her?
Dialogue: 0,01:09:29.04,01:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This story isn't hers alone...
Dialogue: 0,01:09:31.12,01:09:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- ...but all of ours! \N- You people.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:33.04,01:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You got yourself something.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:34.42,01:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what you got now, Chris? \NHow about breaking and entering?
Dialogue: 0,01:09:37.59,01:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By the looks of this, \Na little assault as well.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:40.38,01:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:42.26,01:09:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- This can't go any farther. \N- It won't, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:46.43,01:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, \NI have some 12-year-olds...
Dialogue: 0,01:09:48.77,01:09:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...who cover their tracks \Nbetter than you do.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:51.56,01:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,01:09:53.06,01:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Gucci, do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,01:09:54.81,01:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that my daughter's birth mother?
Dialogue: 0,01:10:02.49,01:10:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look, turn around. \N- What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,01:10:08.04,01:10:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that girl. I did.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:12.25,01:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told she didn't make it \Nthrough the night.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:15.25,01:10:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The night of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:17.46,01:10:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The night of the big fire \Nin Silent Hill.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:21.80,01:10:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There were these people...
Dialogue: 0,01:10:26.14,01:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...these fanatics.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:27.56,01:10:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What they did \Nto that child was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:31.02,01:10:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was 30 years ago, \Nand it's over now.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:34.19,01:10:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as far as I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:36.48,01:10:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it gonna be, city boy?
Dialogue: 0,01:10:38.69,01:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can put you in jail...
Dialogue: 0,01:10:41.40,01:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...or you can go home.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:43.70,01:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's your definition of justice?
Dialogue: 0,01:10:47.58,01:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Many different forms \Nof justice, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:52.04,01:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you've got man's, God's...
Dialogue: 0,01:10:56.08,01:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and even the devil's.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:59.42,01:11:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain forms you just can't control.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:03.13,01:11:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want you to go home now...
Dialogue: 0,01:11:05.72,01:11:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...to your nice warm bed...
Dialogue: 0,01:11:08.18,01:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and let me deal with this town...
Dialogue: 0,01:11:10.81,01:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...and what has happened \Nover the last 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:13.73,01:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? End of story.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:23.78,01:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,DOMINE DEUS OMNIPOTENS IN CUIUS MANU
Dialogue: 0,01:11:28.91,01:11:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me first how you got here.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:33.45,01:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't know \Nhow I got here.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:36.12,01:11:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I've lost my little girl...
Dialogue: 0,01:11:39.21,01:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...and all I know is that \NI'm supposed to be in this church.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:42.05,01:11:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a person of faith?
Dialogue: 0,01:11:44.26,01:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- I love my daughter. \N- That's not what I asked.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:46.93,01:11:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to judge?
Dialogue: 0,01:11:48.26,01:11:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We judge because the souls of history \Nhang in the balance.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:51.68,01:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because our faith \Nhas never failed us.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:53.52,01:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our faith keeps the darkness \Nof hell at bay.
Dialogue: 0,01:11:56.14,01:11:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then use your faith \Nto help me find my little girl.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:00.40,01:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the demon knows where she is.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:02.61,01:12:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me, \Nwhere do I find this demon?
Dialogue: 0,01:12:06.74,01:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has ever returned \Nfrom the core of the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,01:12:09.41,01:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...where the demon lies in wait.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:11.03,01:12:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not gonna help us. \NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:12.66,01:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to face the demon \Nto find your daughter...
Dialogue: 0,01:12:15.41,01:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:16.79,01:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Christabella, they can't go down... \N- Silence, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:23.21,01:12:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps your faith will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:26.34,01:12:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps not.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:42.27,01:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna do this...
Dialogue: 0,01:12:45.49,01:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:48.70,01:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon's adopted...
Dialogue: 0,01:12:51.57,01:12:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'm her mother.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:52.99,01:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that from the moment \NI first laid eyes on her.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:58.41,01:13:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's lucky to have you.
Dialogue: 0,01:13:01.75,01:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother is God in the eyes of a child.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:15.37,01:14:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:17.08,01:14:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in his domain now.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:25.08,01:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this map. Memorize it.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:28.38,01:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your memory may save your life.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:31.92,01:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you see this room? \N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:35.05,01:14:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That is where the darkness lies.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:37.97,01:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon is in the bowels \Nof this building.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:40.56,01:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It hides behind the face \Nof an innocent.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:43.14,01:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean a child?
Dialogue: 0,01:14:44.65,01:14:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't believe your eyes. \NYour eyes will lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:47.11,01:14:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith is the only truth.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:51.24,01:14:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pray for you, Rose...
Dialogue: 0,01:14:52.65,01:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I won't expect you \Nand your friend to return.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:56.78,01:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:00.75,01:15:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:03.33,01:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Left. Right.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:06.54,01:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Left. Left.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:10.09,01:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right. Right. Left. \N- Take them to the lower level.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:14.22,01:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- In the basement? \N- Do it, then return.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:16.22,01:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Left. 3A. \N- But...
Dialogue: 0,01:15:18.76,01:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right. 4A. \N- I said, do it.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:21.18,01:15:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Left. Left. Right. \N- Rose. Rose.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:25.27,01:15:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Left. Right. Left. Left. \N- Rose, she's killing you.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:29.94,01:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rose! \N- Let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:33.28,01:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do this.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:53.46,01:15:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:55.22,01:15:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be drawn to the light, \Nbut you won't be able to see without it.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:01.89,01:16:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:09.98,01:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- So this thing actually works? \N- It will.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:12.98,01:16:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If the demon wants you, it will.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:17.15,01:16:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:19.78,01:16:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lived too long as scavengers. \NI believe this is yours.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:30.08,01:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Witch! Her child's \Nthe likeness of Alessa.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:33.00,01:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Her child's the next vessel.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:34.51,01:16:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop her! \NDon't let the witches go down!
Dialogue: 0,01:16:42.18,01:16:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,01:16:53.32,01:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off her!
Dialogue: 0,01:16:56.82,01:16:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her.
Dialogue: 0,01:16:58.86,01:17:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Wait! Cybil!
Dialogue: 0,01:17:01.70,01:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cybil! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,01:17:26.72,01:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,01:18:58.02,01:18:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,8A.
Dialogue: 0,01:19:00.15,01:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,7 A. Right.
Dialogue: 0,01:19:14.54,01:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. 6A.
Dialogue: 0,01:19:19.21,01:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,4A.
Dialogue: 0,01:19:22.17,01:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,3A.
Dialogue: 0,01:19:26.64,01:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Left, left. Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,01:19:29.56,01:19:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Left, left.
Dialogue: 0,01:24:42.70,01:24:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The child is mine!
Dialogue: 0,01:24:44.79,01:24:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,01:24:52.29,01:24:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mine.
Dialogue: 0,01:24:55.96,01:24:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,01:25:21.82,01:25:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,01:25:26.04,01:25:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the car. Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,01:25:44.18,01:25:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a friendly warning...
Dialogue: 0,01:25:46.72,01:25:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll be back with people \Nwho know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,01:25:52.02,01:25:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you do that, Chris, \NI wanna tell you about Officer Bennett.
Dialogue: 0,01:25:57.36,01:26:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Few years back, some wacko, \Nhe abducted a kid...
Dialogue: 0,01:26:00.57,01:26:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...threw him down a mine vent \Nup there in Silent Hill.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:04.12,01:26:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cybil Bennett, she found that boy.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:06.58,01:26:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She spent three days \Nholding onto him...
Dialogue: 0,01:26:08.50,01:26:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...keeping him alive \Nuntil they were rescued.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:10.87,01:26:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We know what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:12.54,01:26:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:21.47,01:26:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:46.95,01:26:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. \NChristabella, let her live.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:49.37,01:26:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weakness \Nled these souls to judgment.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:51.79,01:26:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- This time you will bear witness. \N- She is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:54.25,01:26:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at her. \NShe's the whelp of your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,01:26:57.46,01:26:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon!
Dialogue: 0,01:26:59.25,01:27:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon fathered this disgusting \Nabomination from her child!
Dialogue: 0,01:27:04.68,01:27:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's mine!
Dialogue: 0,01:27:08.89,01:27:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon. Sharon, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:11.14,01:27:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me. Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:13.94,01:27:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay. \NYour mama's coming.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:18.19,01:27:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again we are called upon \Nto restore innocence.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:22.07,01:27:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We burn this witch. \NWe vanquish evil.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:26.87,01:27:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You can't. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:29.24,01:27:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't let her say this! No! \N- We burn the child!
Dialogue: 0,01:27:32.08,01:27:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight the demon!
Dialogue: 0,01:27:37.29,01:27:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a child!
Dialogue: 0,01:27:38.75,01:27:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck is wrong \Nwith you people?
Dialogue: 0,01:27:42.13,01:27:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,01:27:44.55,01:27:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,01:27:46.97,01:27:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,01:27:49.30,01:27:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who aid the demon...
Dialogue: 0,01:27:51.35,01:27:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...they must be cleansed \Nby the fire from whence they came.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:55.35,01:27:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy. You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:58.69,01:28:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,01:28:01.07,01:28:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you listening to this?
Dialogue: 0,01:28:02.90,01:28:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,01:28:07.03,01:28:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:28:10.16,01:28:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Burn the witch! Burn her! \NBurn the witch!</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:28:22.34,01:28:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,01:28:31.35,01:28:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil witch!
Dialogue: 0,01:28:34.35,01:28:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer.
Dialogue: 0,01:28:40.77,01:28:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:28:43.61,01:28:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Burn the witch! Burn her!</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:28:52.78,01:28:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,01:29:02.29,01:29:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in your own hell.
Dialogue: 0,01:29:12.80,01:29:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, be with me.
Dialogue: 0,01:29:39.92,01:29:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is where the apocalypse began.
Dialogue: 0,01:29:42.00,01:29:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we stopped \Nthe annihilation of the world.
Dialogue: 0,01:29:45.05,01:29:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We drew a line in the sand \Nand said:
Dialogue: 0,01:29:47.71,01:29:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,''Demon, you will not cross!''
Dialogue: 0,01:29:50.38,01:29:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the demon is wicked, \Nfull of treachery.
Dialogue: 0,01:29:54.22,01:29:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet again he comes to tempt us \Nin the guise of an innocent.
Dialogue: 0,01:29:58.60,01:30:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To rid the world of this demon...
Dialogue: 0,01:30:00.81,01:30:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...we must burn this child!
Dialogue: 0,01:30:05.27,01:30:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,01:30:10.32,01:30:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,01:30:12.41,01:30:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, baby. \NEverything's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:15.99,01:30:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:17.91,01:30:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:20.21,01:30:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you people done?
Dialogue: 0,01:30:22.54,01:30:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- You have returned. \N- Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:26.42,01:30:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The witch has returned.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:31.42,01:30:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not believe her lies.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:35.47,01:30:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from a world \Noutside this place.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:37.93,01:30:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from a world full of life!
Dialogue: 0,01:30:43.19,01:30:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:44.90,01:30:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them the truth that you deny, \Neven to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:48.53,01:30:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no apocalypse!
Dialogue: 0,01:30:50.90,01:30:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You burned in the fire \Nthat you started...
Dialogue: 0,01:30:53.11,01:30:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and nothing can save you \Nbecause you're already damned!
Dialogue: 0,01:30:58.29,01:30:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mommy! \N- Take her.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:59.12,01:31:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn her. Burn her as a witch.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:02.08,01:31:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn her! Burn her!
Dialogue: 0,01:31:06.00,01:31:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon witch!
Dialogue: 0,01:31:07.50,01:31:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Burn me? \N- Demon witch.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:09.30,01:31:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:11.80,01:31:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn anything you're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:13.97,01:31:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn anything you can't control.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:18.39,01:31:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman uses your fear \Nto control you.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:22.02,01:31:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She led you to burn \NAlessa Gillespie.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:24.77,01:31:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She led you to burn \Nan innocent child.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:27.81,01:31:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will not deny your guilt...
Dialogue: 0,01:31:31.19,01:31:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you cannot deny her pain!
Dialogue: 0,01:31:33.95,01:31:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That child was sin incarnate.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:37.62,01:31:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's you who have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:42.41,01:31:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You darkened the heart \Nof an innocent...
Dialogue: 0,01:31:45.67,01:31:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and now you cower in the face \Nof Alessa's revenge.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:49.71,01:31:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sinner. \N- Heresy.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:51.88,01:31:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn her. Burn her!
Dialogue: 0,01:31:55.26,01:31:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your faith brings death!
Dialogue: 0,01:32:00.68,01:32:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You are alone in this limbo...
Dialogue: 0,01:32:02.81,01:32:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...and God is not here.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:06.98,01:32:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,01:32:21.41,01:32:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a blasphemer.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:26.29,01:32:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Blasphemer!
Dialogue: 0,01:32:31.71,01:32:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Blasphemer!
Dialogue: 0,01:33:49.12,01:33:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,01:33:51.79,01:33:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've brought the darkness in \Nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,01:33:54.79,01:33:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,01:34:05.97,01:34:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,01:34:12.60,01:34:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,01:34:14.48,01:34:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy. Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:24.63,01:35:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,01:35:55.96,01:36:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Alessa, what have you become?
Dialogue: 0,01:36:14.14,01:36:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,01:36:17.31,01:36:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon! Sharon, honey, it's me. \NIt's Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:42.00,01:36:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Down! We're getting down.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:43.51,01:36:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your eyes. \NShut your eyes, baby.
